➜宁夏农产品金字招牌“中卫硒砂瓜”产品推介会在西安举行
http://www.sohu.com/a/412147570_218913	41563
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200808/bbea4efc58234767a4ea12abf10d5152.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>古人云：西瓜足解渴，割裂青瑶肤。酷暑闷热的夏季，“解暑”成为热词，西瓜荣登“高温消费”热门榜单，宁夏中卫的硒砂瓜成为行业翘楚。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200808/8017feceba8b449eb8239e92e7ca0660.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200808/6e73a4be17cc4c8898cba98c75165621.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
